parameters: Clea: Haa... haa... We've climbed quite a bit, haven't we...
Clea: It seems like the dragon has found an airship.

Thief Nora: Y-Yes... I can hear it... It's the sound of the
dragon flapping its wings!

Mage Relm: The plan up until now has been a success. All
that's left is for us to defeat the dragon!

Priestess Sophia: I still get nervous... I hope we can
communicate with the dragon, if it's someone that humans can
understand.
Clea: Everyone, please raise your fists.
Clea: We don't have time, so please hurry.

Clea: Relm-san, your way of eating is messy. I think it
would be better if you ate more cleanly.
Mage Relm: W-What is it all of a sudden!?

Clea: This is a charm for success that my mother taught me.
It says that if we communicate and tell each other what we
want the other person to fix, everything will go well.

Mage Relm: Um, Nora-san is being too jumpy! She's my genius
friend, so please be more confident!

Thief Nora: Ah, umm! I-I understand! Well, Sophia-san drinks
too much alcohol! It's worrisome!

Priestess Sophia: Clea-chan, you're trying too hard. I think
it's okay to rely more on your friends.
Clea: Yes, thank you very much.

Mage Relm: What is this... It's strange to be fighting
dragons like this!

Thief Nora: Hehe, it's funny, isn't it? Thanks to that, my
shoulder strength is starting to fade away!

Priestess Sophia: Oh my, hehe, isn't it nice... It feels
just like usual.
Clea: It seems like the airship has crashed.

Clea: Let's go for each of our goals and once everything is
finished and settled... let's have a meal.
Clea: Now, let's head towards the dragons.

Explorer Armada: I'm glad you're here. I hope you can lend
me your strength again this time.

Voice Priestess Phoni: Yes, of course! I'm happy to be able
to help everyone.
Clea: Thank you so much for helping us defeat the dragon.
Clea: Let me thank you once again.

Voice Priestess Phoni: No... it's nothing... I just did what
I had to do... there's no need for thanks.

Voice Priestess Phoni: May I ask for one selfish request?
Could you please call me just Phoni today?

Voice Priestess Phoni: Yes! Clea-san! Phoni... sounds
nice... hehehe
Explorer Armada: Is it about time to stop fooling around?

Explorer Armada: Well, from here on out, we'll be climbing
the mountain. It seems to be at a high altitude, so let's be
careful as we proceed.

Explorer Armada: Um, it's not because of me that Valie got
swallowed up by that thing, right...?

Mage Relm: Did you all not notice? It was just for a moment,
but I felt an incredible amount of magic power.

Mage Relm: I believe that thing was erased by that magic
power... I'm trembling even more now that it's become clear.

Thief Nora: I can't hear any more rumbling sounds! So, I
think everything is fine now, probably!
Voice Priestess Phoni: Yes! Everything is fine now!

Explorer Armada: You all are really tough. Then, please
leave your accessories with me for now.

Explorer Armada: Alright, the final piece is in place! I'll
be waiting for everyone in the room with the door.
